OL,3,CTamworth asylum hotel attack: How
OL,4,Conline rumours have real-life
OL,5,Cconsequences
OL,7,FITV News Investigations Editor Daniel
OL,8,FHewitt delivers the second of a
OL,9,Fspecial two-part report into how
OL,10,Fsocial media played a role in an
OL,11,Fattack on a hotel housing asylum
OL,12,Fseekers in Tamworth
OL,14,FIn a small town, news and rumour move
OL,15,Ffast.
OL,17,FSocial media makes it feel smaller,
OL,18,Fspreading it even faster.
