OL,3,CTamworth asylum hotel attack: How
OL,4,Conline rumours have real-life
OL,5,Cconsequences
OL,7,FWhen the Holiday Inn Express in the
OL,8,Fmiddle of Tamworth closed to the
OL,9,Fpublic in late 2022, to be used to
OL,10,Fhouse people going through the asylum
OL,11,Fprocess, it instantly became the topic
OL,12,Fof debate and discussion - largely
OL,13,Fplayed out online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
