OL,3,CTamworth asylum hotel attack: How
OL,4,Conline rumours have real-life
OL,5,Cconsequences
OL,7,FThat was until debate gave way to
OL,8,Fnaked hate and exploded onto the
OL,9,Fstreets. A mob made their way to the
OL,10,Fhotel on August 4 and launched rocks,
OL,11,Ffireworks and petrol bombs at the
OL,12,Fwindows and at the police in an
OL,13,Fattempt to get at the 180 asylum
OL,14,Fseekers inside.
OL,16,FIt was a night that shocked and shamed
OL,17,Feveryone we have spoken to in the
OL,18,Ftown, whatever their view on the
OL,19,Fhotel's use.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
