OL,7,FIt is now empty, "closed for repairs"
OL,8,Freads an A4 sheet on the glass front,
OL,9,Fand it's unclear what will happen
OL,10,Fnext. Is Tamworth now deemed too
OL,11,Funsafe to shelter those seeking
OL,12,Fasylum? Is there fear of further
OL,13,Fbacklash?
OL,15,FWe went to The Lamb - the home of
OL,16,FTamworth Football Club - to speak to
OL,17,Fpeople as they turned up for their
OL,18,Fteam's first home game since the
OL,19,Fattack.
