OL,7,FEveryone expresses their shock at the
OL,8,Flevel of violence, but there's little
OL,9,Fenthusiasm for the hotel returning to
OL,10,Fits previous role of housing asylum
OL,11,Fseekers.
OL,13,F"I don't like it, and I'm not gonna
OL,14,Fsay stand here and say I do," one
OL,15,Fyoung man tells me.
OL,17,F"I also don't think the violence that
OL,18,Fwas there was needed because it put a
OL,19,Fbad light on Tamworth.
