OL,7,F"If people are coming into the country
OL,8,Fand they're not working, then you
OL,9,Fknow, why are we letting them come in?"
OL,11,FAsylum seekers are not legally allowed
OL,12,Fto work in the UK while going through
OL,13,Fthe asylum process, except in very
OL,14,Flimited circumstances. When I put this
OL,15,Fto him, he asks: "So why are they here
OL,16,Fthen? Do they want to work? Because I
OL,17,Fdon't believe they do."
OL,19,FPeople seek asylum for all sorts of
OL,20,Freasons, including fleeing wars, but
OL,21,Fwhen I put that to him he replies:
