OL,7,F"But it's not necessarily all about
OL,8,Fthat though, is it? It's not fleeing
OL,9,Fwars. A lot of it is fleeing because
OL,10,Fit's an easy life over here. It's a
OL,11,Fgolden ticket."
OL,13,FThat is not how 17-year-old Dylan
OL,14,Ffeels, who we meet away from the
OL,15,Ffootball in the town centre.
