OL,7,FLike lots of people here, he learned
OL,8,Fof the attack on the hotel through
OL,9,Fposts on social media - and he
OL,10,Fbelieves it is where his generation is
OL,11,Fpicking up misinformation about asylum
OL,12,Fimmigration.
OL,14,F"I'm ashamed to live in Tamworth
OL,15,Fbecause of what has just happened," he
OL,16,Ftold me.
