OL,7,F"The asylum seekers needed a place to
OL,8,Fstay. I would let them stay because
OL,9,Fthey would've done the same if we were
OL,10,Fin that position. We are lucky that we
OL,11,Fare not.
OL,13,F"And they, they had found somewhere
OL,14,Fthat they thought was safe for them
OL,15,Fand then this has happened and scared
OL,16,Fthem."
OL,18,FDylan though does not think he speaks
OL,19,Ffor the majority of his generation in
OL,20,FTamworth.
