OL,7,F"No, and obviously with social media,
OL,8,Fit's just going to carry on, and it
OL,9,Fwon't stop until someone actually does
OL,10,Fsomething about it," he said.
OL,12,FIt is striking the amount of people we
OL,13,Fhave met in Tamworth referring to
OL,14,Fposts they have seen on social media
OL,15,Flinked to asylum seekers staying at
OL,16,Fthe hotel, particularly on one popular
OL,17,Fonline community group with over
OL,18,F50,000 followers.
