OL,7,FThe park behind the hotel is a
OL,8,Fparticular source of rumour, and there
OL,9,Fwe met Lesley, looking after her
OL,10,Fgrandchildren. She says social media
OL,11,Fhas a lot to answer for.
OL,13,F"Because of social media, different
OL,14,Fthings people have put on there,
OL,15,Fsaying: 'Don't go down the park, don't
OL,16,Fgo to the Snow Dome because there's
OL,17,Fpeople there, there's men, you know,
OL,18,Fthey're watching children.' So I think
OL,19,Fit was inevitable.
OL,21,F"I think all of this is just hearsay."
