OL,7,FHe was staying in the hotel on the
OL,8,Fnight of the riot, and so unlike those
OL,9,Fwho were resident there, he has not
OL,10,Fbeen moved out of Tamworth, a town he
OL,11,Fsays has been made almost impossible
OL,12,Fto live in because of online hate.
OL,14,F"People believe anything that happens
OL,15,Fin the social media," he said.
OL,17,F"We're just trying to live in this
OL,18,Ftown, which the government have put us
OL,19,Fin. It wasn't chosen by us.
