OL,7,F"These people don't like us. It
OL,8,Fdoesn't matter what we are. So (I feel
OL,9,Fat) any time they might attack us or
OL,10,Faccuse us of anything, even if it's
OL,11,Fnot our fault.
OL,13,F"So we are always, especially me,
OL,14,Fliving in fear every day."
OL,16,FThe riot has had ripples across this
OL,17,Fcommunity, and its impact is still
OL,18,Fbeing felt.
