OL,7,FThey are black people in an
OL,8,Foverwhelmingly white town - 96% of
OL,9,FTamworth's population is White
OL,10,FBritish, compared to 83% of the UK
OL,11,Fpopulation.
OL,13,FMaxine has lived here 32 years and
OL,14,Fsaid the riot was "not the Tamworth I
OL,15,Fknow".
