OL,4,Conline rumours have real-life
OL,5,Cconsequences
OL,7,FThe violence has profoundly impacted
OL,8,F18-year-old Nigel and his family. He
OL,9,Fis from South Africa, and his mum
OL,10,Fworks as a mobile carer. She is now
OL,11,Fworried about travelling around the
OL,12,Ftown, and even more worried about her
OL,13,Fson.
OL,15,F"She was really scared to go out to
OL,16,Fwork," Ethan told me.
OL,18,F"She messaged the people at work to
OL,19,Ftell them could they change the
OL,20,Flocation for where she was working
OL,21,Fbecause of what's happening, you know?
