OL,7,F"I think it's really affected not only
OL,8,Fmy mum, but also everyone else that
OL,9,Flives here.
OL,11,F"I'm the only black person at my
OL,12,Ffootball club, so every time I go out,
OL,13,F(my mum) be worried about me, going
OL,14,Fout, paranoid saying 'no, don't go'".
OL,16,FA month on from the attack at the
OL,17,Fhotel, 63 people have been arrested
OL,18,Fand across Staffordshire 25 have been
OL,19,Fcharged.
