OL,3,CTamworth asylum hotel attack: How
OL,4,Conline rumours have real-life
OL,5,Cconsequences
OL,7,FThe tiny minority of people who rioted
OL,8,Fon August 4th do not represent the
OL,9,Fpeople of this town or their views.
OL,11,FThe view we heard again and again was
OL,12,Fof local concern about the closure of
OL,13,Ftheir hotel for use by the Home
OL,14,FOffice, with little consultation or
OL,15,Finformation, being hijacked by hate -
OL,16,For as one man put it to us: by
OL,17,F"f****** idiots jumping on the
OL,18,Fbandwagon".
